title: MisterMusic Show 346 - new indie,alternative, rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show #346 (2 hours) 192kbps MP3-



New tunes this week from Best Coast, The Elwins, Agent Fresco, and another new song by Death Cab For Cutie.

We travel back to March 1992 for the 'Oldie of the Week'. A song that remained number one on the US modern rock charts for a total of 5 weeks that year.

It's a blend of new indie and alternative music with classic hits from the past-
The MisterMusic Show.



The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
